metadata.description:
■Women Of The Sun #0101-0130 / Theme : The Sun

We are the sun. We are the light to the future. We are hope. We are the rainbow. We are colores. Just being ourselves, we all are precious and beautiful. You have the power to shine, you are the sun to shine yourself.

Check Women Of The Sun : Genesis #0001-0100→ https://opensea.io/collection/women-of-the-sun-genesis

太陽のように輝く力を持っている
私を照らす太陽は私だ
